## `test_symlinks_survive_reopen(tmp_db)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-symlinks-15 -->

### Postconditions

```python
from sqlite_fs import mkfs, open_fs

mkfs(str(tmp_db))
fs = open_fs(str(tmp_db))
with fs.as_user(0, 0):
    fs.symlink(b"/persisted/target", "/link")
fs.close()

fs = open_fs(str(tmp_db))
with fs.as_user(0, 0):
    assert fs.readlink("/link") == b"/persisted/target"
fs.close()
```

